name: Sexy Cop Uniform
description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

To support me you can buy me a coffe at https://ko-fi.com/antonioriolo

Training settings:

33 images, 25 steps, 9 epochs, you find many epochs (with test images using plot xy script) on my Patreon while supporting me.


Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.5-0.8

  • Keys: wearing sexy cop uniform

I'm not very happy about this model. It doesn't work as i expected.

First advice i give you it's to put a big weight on the keyword, like "(wearing sexy cop uniform:1.5)" and use always the model with atleast a 0.5-0.6 weight or you will see a bikini girl with a cop cap hat.

You can prompt something like "blue uniform" or "black uniform" to have different types of cop uniform (other then different colors)

One other thing that have worked is to start the prompt with "a woman next to a police car". As you can see from some example images.

I also tryied to had handcuffs and cop glasses as keywords but they do not seem to work, atleast i didn't manage to let them work. Handcuffs keyword produce nonsense, cop glasses produce normal glasses, even if there are many training images with cop glasses.

My mistake might be that i had to do more steps to train something like this, but i'm not sure that it could give a better result.

Anyway, problems aside, if you follow the weight instructions, you will end up with some good sexy cop images, Enjoy!

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians
